{"tid":2202776,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼政府出狠招 拒戴口罩者被罰為武漢肺炎死者挖墳墓","createTime":"2020-09-15T00:28:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T00:42:07.000Z","uid":123774,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f1ae730a0dd9b83f7e7f282279f80312410045c3","tid":2202776,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T00:28:41.000Z","msg":"據《每日郵報》9月14日報道，在印度尼西亞爪哇東部，拒絕戴口罩的人都會被懲罰去為新冠肺炎死者挖墳墓。<br />\n<br />\n在格雷西克地區，8名拒絕戴口罩的人被要求在Ngabetan村的一個公共墓地挖墳墓作為懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n上週三，地區負責人Suyono說:「目前只有三個掘墓人，所以我想我應該讓這些人和他們一起工作。」<br />\n<br />\n當地新冠肺炎病例持續增加，促使該村加強安全措施。無視新規定的居民將依法受到罰款或社區服務的懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>P.S. 係East Java, 唔係成個印尼</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8729991/Anyone-refusing-wear-mask-dig-GRAVES-Covid-19-victims-punishment-East-Java.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-8729991%2FAnyone-refusing-wear-mask-dig-GRAVES-Covid-19-victims-punishment-East-Java.html&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacQEOIADdcgve6BSnlMLQ7pQ%3D&h=b568e88b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8729991/Anyone-refusing-wear-mask-dig-GRAVES-Covid-19-victims-punishment-East-Java.html</a>"},{"pid":"88fed2583fb223bd5b84bb215a849544ff6c0525","tid":2202776,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T00:42:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}